overview.en: The CSCY exchange network is the abbreviation of Cloud Store Chain. The Cloud Store Chain is an underlying protocol based on blockchain development and a cross-chain public chain based on decentralized architecture.
overview.zh: CSCY通兑网络是云店链（Cloud Store Chain）的简称，云店链（Cloud Store Chain）是基于区块链开发的底层协议，建立在去中心化架构上的跨链公链。
